column.Name: ImageFileType
column.lookupquery: SELECT ImageFileTypeID, ImageFileType FROM pImageFileType WHERE Active=1 ORDER BY ImageFileType

column.Name: ImageSubFolder1
column.lookupquery: SELECT ImageType, ImageType AS ImageTypeName FROM pImageType ORDER BY ImageType

column.Name: ImageSubFolder2
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM iCustom1 div INNER JOIN fnx_Permissions_GetGuidProductTypePermissions('##TEAMID##', 26) access ON access.ProductTypeId = div.CustomID AND access.PermissionRoleID > 0 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: ImageSubFolder3
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM iCustom2 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: ImageSubFolder4
column.lookupquery: SELECT * FROM iCustom3 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: ImageSubFolder5
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM iCustom4 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: ImageSubFolder6
column.lookupquery: SELECT * FROM xCustom1 ORDER BY CustomKey
